should be treated more harshly than north and former national 
security adviser robert mcfarlane who also were sentenced to 
probation in the affair 
i deeply regret not being more candid with congressional 
investigators about the enterprise and north secord told the 
judge if i could correct this i certainly would i will regret 
it for the rest of my life 
the enterprise was the maze of offshore companies and swiss bank 
accounts in the irancontra scandal from which money was withdrawn 
by secord to pay for norths home security system 
green said he and secord were very pleased with the sentence 
and that secord is now in a position to get on with his life 
secord was assessed a standard 50 in court costs 
weingarten told the judge that secord unlike north and 
mcfarlane had the benefit of personal legal counsel before making 
