syrian officers the military source said 
hrawi appointed lahoud commander nov 24 after he was elected 
president by parliament 
hrawi also dismissed rebellious christian gen michel aoun as 
commanderinchief of the armed forces and interim prime minister 
but aoun refused to leave the presidential palace 
