sen ernest f hollings dsc proposed to replace revenues from 
the reduced social security taxes with a national sales tax 
there is no sleight of hand whatsoever moynihan replied 
and i do not see that there was any need to make such a 
characterization 
lawmakers from both parties have expressed displeasure that 
