vandalism 
the painter whos taken the pseudonym mandrake after the 
comicstrip magician said billboard ads in predominantly black and 
hispanic neighborhoods on the south side are aimed at young people 
and promote dangerous vices 
mandrake who described himself as a 54yearold black 
professional but declined to give his real name said hes taken a 
paintbrush to billboards three times in broad daylight because the 
