billy was as in the past the nurse asked the young woman to 
signal if she could hear this time miss jennings raised her 
eyebrows 
when i saw her i felt such a relief mrs jennings said of 
her first visit with her daughter after she had awakened my 
heart was so full it felt like it would burst 
by that afternoon miss jennings was off her ventilator on 
