of any social security tax cut be put into such retirement accounts 
thats risky business a suggestion that social security be 
changed into a private voluntary system dug the republicans into 
trouble on the issue more than 25 years ago and theyve been 
trying to dig out ever since barry goldwater the 1964 republican 
