we try to be sane said david schoenwald who runs new 
alternatives an environmental and alternativeenergy mutual fund 
that rose 26 percent last year were not a big enterprise 
nothing fancy were very plain vanilla we buy only american 
stocks no options no hedging when we buy a stock we hope we can 
keep it forever 
